AP Top U.S. News at 10:13 a.m. EST
03 Nov 2019, 04:00 by EndPlay
Airbnb bans 'party houses' after California shooting kills 5
Dow says no injuries at site of explosion in Louisiana
Crews make progress on large Southern California wildfire
US judge blocks Trump's health insurance rule for immigrants
Illinois marijuana law aims to undo harm of war on the drug
AP-NORC poll: More support than oppose impeachment probe
Syrian refugee turns to food to rebuild his life in US
Au revoir to daylight saving time, but not a goodbye
Houston mayor's race: crime, flooding, Trump are all issues
Service to be held in NC for former US Sen. Kay Hagan
